{"tid":392115,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛蓮說","createTime":"2017-09-08T09:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T10:47:26.000Z","uid":389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9993c8273ab2237d0d58ff2f4d4cfc16339aac7f","tid":392115,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"水陸草木之花，可愛者甚蕃。[1]晉陶淵明獨愛菊。[2]自李唐來，世人甚愛牡丹。[3]予獨愛蓮之出淤泥而不染，[4]濯清漣而不妖；[5]中通外直，[6]不蔓不枝；香遠益清，[7]亭亭淨植，可遠觀而不可褻玩焉。[8]<br />\n<br />\n予謂：菊，[9]花之隱逸者也；[10]牡丹，花之富貴者也；[11]蓮，[12]花之君子者也。[13]噫！菊之愛，[14]陶後鮮有聞。[15]蓮之愛，同予者何人？[16]牡丹之愛，宜乎眾矣！[17]"},{"pid":"401ed0b9c6a6b4de607c7c9b926aa2d37997eb3c","tid":392115,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"可遠觀而不可褻玩焉。"},{"pid":"606b5802a564331739984e676a2b9cf8cdaeef42","tid":392115,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"最撚憎仆街蓮花"},{"pid":"e4ccc65a3a873b224b7cb40408898c277f7e11be","tid":392115,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚憎仆街蓮花</blockquote><br />\n予獨愛蓮之出淤泥而不染，濯清漣而不妖<br />\n<br />\n君子不器，遠小人而親賢人"},{"pid":"989d56ec25c245bc782d027833f16db65d7978ee","tid":392115,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"中通外直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0061efcbb1b63c6474ad622bf671536769dfadcc","tid":392115,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:46:20.000Z","msg":"岩岩通靈，得到另一篇<br />\n<br />\n屈原曰：「吾聞之，新沐者必彈冠(11)，新浴者必振衣(12)。安能以身之察察，受物之汶汶(13)者乎！寧赴湘流，葬於江魚之腹中，安能以皓皓(14)之白，而蒙世俗之塵埃乎！」<br />\n<br />\n漁父莞爾而笑，鼓枻(15)而去，乃歌曰：「滄浪(16)之水清兮，可以濯吾纓(17)；滄浪之水濁兮，可以濯吾足。」遂去，不復與言。"},{"pid":"417821ea817e55f7eb96de289713bbecf9e5859b","tid":392115,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"可以話係心路歷程<br />\n<br />\n不想同流合污，隨波逐流，便以死明志"},{"pid":"437611ab9df5eb1c15f93715bbec863109526b84","tid":392115,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"老蓮說"},{"pid":"f7e953ed240942d839011367f6ffa9de9e3061ff","tid":392115,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中通外直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n內通中國, 但送子女去外國讀書咁解<br />\n<br />\n利申: 中文攞U"},{"pid":"8bad862b46f49f22539d9e8a50ece73c3ebea5d9","tid":392115,"uid":41765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"Irene says <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}